{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe4017f298","title":"给李钠的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1a05d09663","index":0,"year":1963,"month":1,"day":4,"articleId":"fe4017f298"},{"id":"a649148d81","index":1,"year":1963,"month":1,"day":15,"articleId":"fe4017f298"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"61ffb686ef","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李内，毛泽东的女儿。当时在北京大学历史系读书。"},{"id":"bb3919a7e1","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"秋水篇，即《庄子·秋水》。李纳当时在学校里正学习《古代汉语》中“庄子”课程。"},{"id":"28aa79f867","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"河伯，传说中的黄河水神，《庄子·秋水》中的主人公之一。"}],"contents":[{"id":"66fe4877a9","type":"title","text":"给李钠的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298"},{"id":"61ffb686ef","type":"paragraph","text":"李内娃：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298"},{"id":"bb3919a7e1","type":"paragraph","text":"刚发一信，就接了你的信。喜感无极。你痛苦、忧伤，是极好事，从此你就有希望了。痛苦、优伤，表示你认真想事，争上游、鼓干劲，一定可以转到翘尾巴、自以为是、孤碎、看不起人的反面去，主动权就到了你的手里了。没人管你了，靠你自己管自己，这就好了，这是大学比中学的好处。中学也有两种人，有社会经验的孩子；有娇生惯养的所谓干部子弟，你就吃了这个亏。现在好了，干部子弟（翘尾巴的）吃不开了，尾巴翘不成了，痛苦来了，改变态度也就来了，这就好了。读了秋水篇，好，你不会再做河伯时了，为你祝贺！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298"},{"id":"28aa79f867","type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298"},{"id":"d10f9d3bed","type":"paragraph","text":"一月四日李内娃：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298"},{"id":"43cf5804ab","type":"paragraph","text":"信收到，极高兴。大有起色，大有壮志雄心，大有自我批评，大有痛苦、伤心，都是极好的。你从此站立起来了。因此我极为念你，为你祝贺。读浅，不急，合群，开朗，多与同学们多谈，交心，学人之长，克己之短，大有可为","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298"},{"id":"3a48abfb37","type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298"},{"id":"842c835c81","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十五日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298"}],"page":{"id":"1ce6628cb0","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"fe4017f298","start":327,"end":328}}}},"__N_SSG":true}